{"tid":1156834,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[3D+多人連線] 任天堂為即將在6月28日發售的《Super Mario Maker 2》舉行發佈會","createTime":"2019-05-16T00:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T09:43:26.000Z","uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38ad10c31ae3406c7c2579f4734fbd0d96102fcc","tid":1156834,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:52:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://greatgame.asia/《mario-maker-2》線上發佈會-公開大量未知新情報/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2F%E3%80%8Amario-maker-2%E3%80%8B%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5%E6%96%B0%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%2F&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=3c4ed523\" target=\"_blank\">https://greatgame.asia/《mario-maker-2》線上發佈會-公開大量未知新情報/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《Mario Maker 2》線上發佈會 公開大量未知新情報</strong><br />\n游雲  31<br />\n<br />\n任天堂於今早6:00(日本時間7:00)舉行了「Nintendo Direct」，公佈了即將在6月28日發售的《Super Mario Maker 2(超級瑪利歐創作家 2)》大量全新情報，當中要最令人留意的是，今次官方公佈了遊戲片加上12月個人任天堂網絡服務，日版只需6,980日圓，還有「Nintendo Switch 點觸筆」作預購特典(繁體中文版也有)，至於美版則為69.99美元，美版預購特典方面則未有公佈，大家在選購時可要留意一下。<br />\n<br />\n日版視頻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ct1GwHvNKME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dct1GwHvNKME&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=d14fa98b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ct1GwHvNKME</a><br />\n<br />\n美版視頻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jPi-u0D8sQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjPi-u0D8sQ4&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=db877068\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jPi-u0D8sQ4</a><br />\n<br />\n今次的作品中，一開始便介紹了玩法部份，玩家可自行創作出各式各樣的瑪利歐關卡，當中將收錄了原有的《超級瑪利歐兄弟》、《超級瑪利歐兄弟3》、《超級瑪利歐世界》以及《超級瑪利歐兄弟Wii U》等遊戲風格外，今次更會收錄《超級瑪利歐世界3D》，亦會追加當中登場的貓貓瑪利歐，讓玩家可創作出一個非常精彩的3D遊戲世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img921/8347/7N9C6t.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg921%2F8347%2F7N9C6t.jpg%3F&h=4080ed63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片段中亦有提及今次追加的新元素部份，首先在關卡背景方面，迎追加了沙漠、雪原、森林以及空中，還可自行設定日與夜，此外在地形方面亦追加了斜坡部份，裹可配合分鏡功能來令畫面變得更流暢。此外，亦有一些是用來刁難玩家的部份，好像太陽、蛇形磚塊、ON/OFF磚塊及平衡板穿等等，令遊戲能設計的地方變得更多及具吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img923/9164/4FsrHy.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg923%2F9164%2F4FsrHy.jpg%3F&h=879b4c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>玩家可自行設計遊戲的分鏡移動，令畫面變得更流暢</em><br />\n<br />\n除了一般的遊戲設計外，今次玩家可自行設計出不同分數的金幣給其他玩家收集，分別有10分、30分及50分，讓設計者能因應難提來供玩家收集，而且遊戲更支援二人合作設計，讓玩家能與朋友一起合力創作關卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img924/8028/TTY50k.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg924%2F8028%2FTTY50k.jpg%3F&h=30bd0447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於連線機能方面，今次將追加多人連線的功能，最多可同時四位玩家一起遊玩，加上超豐富的大量新元素，在推出時應該又會引起一遍創作關卡熱潮了吧！"},{"pid":"7b2e3ac947e715d85caf29a7cb381ca303e09c67","tid":1156834,"uid":243960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"補充：<br />\n最新影片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eKkyCy5Bur4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeKkyCy5Bur4&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=2c571b9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eKkyCy5Bur4</a><br />\n<br />\nWiki: <a href=\"https://www.mariowiki.com/Super_Mario_Maker_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mariowiki.com%2FSuper_Mario_Maker_2&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=63a425f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mariowiki.com/Super_Mario_Maker_2</a>"},{"pid":"5b78fca64ecd4bf8b4336f4e235b7bfcce1bed2e","tid":1156834,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}